bq. the taskid will be new
Not new. NNBench uses a sequential id in the task id (1, 2, ...)  instead of the entire task id.
{code}
      int taskId =
          TaskAttemptID.forName(conf.get(MRJobConfig.TASK_ATTEMPT_ID))
              .getTaskID().getId();
{code}
